phase2.explanation:
🤖 **Common ViewModel with Compose mistakes.**

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| Multiple state flows | Use single UI state |
| Direct mutation | Use `update { }` |
| No UI State | Define `data class UiState` |
| Heavy work | Use coroutines |
| No error handling | Add error state |

**Fixes:**
```kotlin
// 1. Single UI state
data class UiState(
    val user: User? = null,
    val isLoading: Boolean = false,
    val error: String? = null
)

// 2. Use update
fun updateUser(user: User) {
    _uiState.update { it.copy(user = user) }
}

// 3. Handle all states
if (uiState.isLoading) { /* loading */ }
if (uiState.error != null) { /* error */ }

// 4. Use viewModelScope
viewModelScope.launch {
    // Heavy work
}
```

